# GCP Hackathon Requirements

## Event

- DevOps × AI Agent Hackathon 2026
- Submission: 2026-07-10
- Hashtag: `#findy_hackathon`

## Required Google Cloud Tech

- **Runtime**: Cloud Run (required)
- **AI**: Gemini API + ADK (Agents Development Kit) (required)
- Optional Phase 2: Speech-to-Text, Text-to-Speech

## Submission Checklist

1. Public GitHub repository URL
2. Deployed project URL (working demo)
3. Proto Pedia registration URL

## DevOps Expectations

- GitHub Actions CI on PR/push
- Staging deploy to Cloud Run on main
- Prompt forbidden-word check in CI
- README must document deploy URL and demo steps

## Architecture Defaults

- API: `services/api/` → Cloud Run service `nakanaori-api`
- Web: `services/web/` → Cloud Run service `nakanaori-web` (or combined for MVP)
- Secrets: GCP Secret Manager for `GEMINI_API_KEY` (never commit)

## Judging Alignment

- Agent must be central (multi-step workflow, not single chat)
- Show DevOps cycle: build → test → deploy → monitor
- Demo scenario: see `docs/demo-scenario.md`
